des:
Dog age uses the latest science to tell you how old your dog is in human years!

Did you think your dog age in human years was just their age times 7? It's not that simple! Learn your dog's true human age with this skill!

Learn more about the science behind this skill here: https://www.sciencefocus.com/news/new-trick-to-calculate-your-old-dogs-age/
